{"tid":522133,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"純討論，不要行動。鎖住部單車算唔算犯法？","createTime":"2018-01-07T09:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T10:55:27.000Z","uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"778d21133890897ef90ed63eed978388fb3f59d9","tid":522133,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:14:52.000Z","msg":"部單車唔係我既"},{"pid":"0de90541e2a5a8fa13607c2cb8c8f3bdcfdeeb17","tid":522133,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"778d21133890897ef90ed63eed978388fb3f59d9","tid":522133,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:14:52.000Z","msg":"部單車唔係我既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"刑事毀壞？"},{"pid":"a17f87f7f5ff3443dfb1cece837f9f2676532761","tid":522133,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>部單車唔係我既</blockquote>刑事毀壞？</blockquote><br />\n部車無壞仲算唔算毀壞？🤔"},{"pid":"89bca6007b1efce8659a86fc2abd49f60841779f","tid":522133,"uid":53568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"好問題 <br />\n刑事毀壞唔中 因為佢無損壞<br />\n禁錮唔中因為唔適用係死物<br />\n第228章40條所列既妨擾罪都無條岩<br />\n所以其實應應該係無犯法<br />\n除非你破壞到佢架單車<br />\n或姐你鎖既過程中俾佢見到 恐嚇佢<br />\n或姐鎖既過程斷正 俾人用遊蕩罪指稱你引起他人不安<br />\n如果唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffad2e157bec0efbcbeb2a1b3770965fae436ff1","tid":522133,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17f87f7f5ff3443dfb1cece837f9f2676532761","tid":522133,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>部單車唔係我既</blockquote>刑事毀壞？</blockquote><br />\n部車無壞仲算唔算毀壞？🤔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"刑事毀壞是刑事罪行之一，毀壞即是破壞，即是未經授權，將物件的形狀、顏色、<span style=\"color: red;\">或原有功能改變</span>。<br />\n<br />\n應該算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbb2c0ac23316aaba2015d38a3b8f5d08c2b865","tid":522133,"uid":31708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffad2e157bec0efbcbeb2a1b3770965fae436ff1","tid":522133,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17f87f7f5ff3443dfb1cece837f9f2676532761","tid":522133,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>部單車唔係我既</blockquote>刑事毀壞？</blockquote><br />\n部車無壞仲算唔算毀壞？🤔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"刑事毀壞是刑事罪行之一，毀壞即是破壞，即是未經授權，將物件的形狀、顏色、<span style=\"color: red;\">或原有功能改變</span>。<br />\n<br />\n應該算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"鎖左部單車姐 個鎖可以剪可以拆 唔會有手尾 亦唔會改變用途架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878073d8505b1e26f59c1607fa79f9151497932e","tid":522133,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffad2e157bec0efbcbeb2a1b3770965fae436ff1","tid":522133,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17f87f7f5ff3443dfb1cece837f9f2676532761","tid":522133,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>部單車唔係我既</blockquote>刑事毀壞？</blockquote><br />\n部車無壞仲算唔算毀壞？🤔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"刑事毀壞是刑事罪行之一，毀壞即是破壞，即是未經授權，將物件的形狀、顏色、<span style=\"color: red;\">或原有功能改變</span>。<br />\n<br />\n應該算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"咁屋村保安鎖你車又係刑事毀壞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ce29ec8e9d3af7ff58cc9652c816ccbabc38da","tid":522133,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"不要問，只要做<br />\n法官未判之前都唔算犯法"},{"pid":"56a72245906077f3a018f36309667a9d9f96155d","tid":522133,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T21:26:24.000Z","msg":"我剩係知佢爆你鎖就係佢犯法<br />\n<br />\n好似同呢個case幾似<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=4Hjs%2BmuqsxpMn9N80J9o0gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f3d9da36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 違例泊車屢見不鮮，觀塘一個地盤近日出辣招對付違泊車輛，一批以「巨石陣」對付違泊的圖片在網上瘋傳，從相片可見，有人以吊臂車搬動多座巨石「圍困」違泊車輛，令違泊車輛變成有入無出，藉以懲戒違泊。由於巨石相當沉重，相信單憑司機一人之力無法移走巨石，車輛紛紛被困在地盤。有網民直言「巨石陣」相當有用，相信司機不敢再在於該地盤違例泊車。 <br />\n有網民笑言，在屋邨屋苑違泊被鎖車，解鎖費為300、400元，但違泊司機遇上「巨石陣」，「解鎖費」分分鐘可能要高達1,000元，因司機需租用吊臂車吊起巨石，形容此地盤出招「快、狠、準」，相信違泊問題會迎刃而解。有網民指，該地盤曾張貼告示呼籲司機不要違泊，但效果未如理想，「係都要迫人出手！」相信司機亦無話可說。"},{"pid":"7f41f83e68fb71e29d89a1b5f48a159ac059de6d","tid":522133,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bbb2c0ac23316aaba2015d38a3b8f5d08c2b865","tid":522133,"uid":31708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffad2e157bec0efbcbeb2a1b3770965fae436ff1","tid":522133,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17f87f7f5ff3443dfb1cece837f9f2676532761","tid":522133,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>部單車唔係我既</blockquote>刑事毀壞？</blockquote><br />\n部車無壞仲算唔算毀壞？🤔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"刑事毀壞是刑事罪行之一，毀壞即是破壞，即是未經授權，將物件的形狀、顏色、<span style=\"color: red;\">或原有功能改變</span>。<br />\n<br />\n應該算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"鎖左部單車姐 個鎖可以剪可以拆 唔會有手尾 亦唔會改變用途架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:05:47.000Z","msg":"鎖左架單車 架車郁唔到 <br />\n應該算改變左用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加上刑事係無整返好就無手尾呢一回事"},{"pid":"e3944be071179429f46c3ddd1c1c6bb56b07fb47","tid":522133,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"878073d8505b1e26f59c1607fa79f9151497932e","tid":522133,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffad2e157bec0efbcbeb2a1b3770965fae436ff1","tid":522133,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17f87f7f5ff3443dfb1cece837f9f2676532761","tid":522133,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>部單車唔係我既</blockquote>刑事毀壞？</blockquote><br />\n部車無壞仲算唔算毀壞？🤔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"刑事毀壞是刑事罪行之一，毀壞即是破壞，即是未經授權，將物件的形狀、顏色、<span style=\"color: red;\">或原有功能改變</span>。<br />\n<br />\n應該算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"咁屋村保安鎖你車又係刑事毀壞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:06:15.000Z","msg":"果到有無寫明唔拍得先"},{"pid":"b28d44bb298112fd737bec53268c1e2efbbf864a","tid":522133,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:14:00.000Z","msg":"衰盜竊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n盜竊罪的基本定義<br />\n(1)如任何人不誠實地挪佔屬於另一人的財產，<span style=\"color: red;\">意圖永久地剝奪該另一人的財產，即屬犯盜竊罪</span>，而竊賊 (thief)及偷竊 (steal)亦須據此解釋。<br />\n(2)作出挪佔的<span style=\"color: red;\">目的不論是為了獲益，或是為了該竊賊本身的利益，均屬無關重要。</span>"},{"pid":"d0a12d7074a833cbc80ce4cd93a901124f6aacb6","tid":522133,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"拿 居苑鎖車就無事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af12f1f2faf7fb64a5fd2debe925e4f3d5020325","tid":522133,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拿 居苑鎖車就無事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁如果部車泊係私人地方<br />\n可唔可以搵人拖走佢部車再問車主拎拖車費"}]}